ure has been carefully assessed. We present the derived set of\ncorrected mode characteristics, discuss their uncertainties and the precision\nof the ridge to mode correction schemes. In our conclusions, we address how to\nfurther improve these estimates, and the implications for other data sets, like\nGONG+ and HMI.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Sep 2012 02:39:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
