as successfully applied to simulations and experiments on\ncolloidal hard sphere systems [I. Gazuz et. al., Phys. Rev. Lett. 102, 248302\n(2009)], while we provide detailed information on its derivation and general\nproperties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Sep 2012 10:27:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 25 Feb 2013 12:37:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
